@startuml
title Успешный сценарий: Создание бага и назначение исполнителя

actor "Тестировщик" as QA
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Bug Service" as BugSvc
participant "Assignment Service" as AssignSvc
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
queue "Event Bus\n(RabbitMQ)" as Bus
participant "Notification\nWorker" as NotifyWorker
participant "Email/Slack\nService" as NotifyApi

== Транзакция №1: Создание бага ==

QA -> Gateway: POST /api/bugs\n{title: "Падение при загрузке",\npriority: "HIGH", project_id: "PIS-WEB"}
activate Gateway

Gateway -> Gateway: Аутентификация\nи авторизация
Gateway -> BugSvc: Пересылка запроса
activate BugSvc

BugSvc -> BugSvc: Валидация данных\n(заголовок, приоритет, вложения)

BugSvc -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
activate DB

BugSvc -> DB: INSERT INTO bugs\n(id, title, priority, status)\nVALUES ('BUG-2026-0117', ...,'OPEN')
DB --> BugSvc: OK

BugSvc -> DB: INSERT INTO bug_attachments\n(bug_id='BUG-2026-0117', ...)
DB --> BugSvc: OK

BugSvc -> DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION
DB --> BugSvc: Committed
deactivate DB

BugSvc -> Bus: publish(BugCreated,\nbug_id='BUG-2026-0117')
activate Bus
Bus --> BugSvc: ACK
deactivate Bus

BugSvc --> Gateway: 201 Created\n{bug_id: "BUG-2026-0117",\nstatus: "OPEN"}
deactivate BugSvc

Gateway --> QA: 201 Created\n{bug_id, status}
deactivate Gateway

== Транзакция №2: Назначение исполнителя ==

QA -> Gateway: POST /api/bugs/BUG-2026-0117/assign
activate Gateway

Gateway -> AssignSvc: Пересылка запроса
activate AssignSvc

AssignSvc -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
activate DB

AssignSvc -> DB: SELECT * FROM users\nWHERE role='DEVELOPER'\nAND status='AVAILABLE'\nLIMIT 1 FOR UPDATE
DB --> AssignSvc: dev.volkov

AssignSvc -> DB: INSERT INTO bug_assignments\n(bug_id, user_id)\nVALUES ('BUG-2026-0117','dev.volkov')
DB --> AssignSvc: OK

AssignSvc -> DB: UPDATE bugs\nSET status='IN_PROGRESS'\nWHERE id='BUG-2026-0117'
DB --> AssignSvc: OK

AssignSvc -> DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION
DB --> AssignSvc: Committed
deactivate DB

AssignSvc -> Bus: publish(BugAssigned,\nbug_id='BUG-2026-0117', assignee='dev.volkov')
activate Bus
Bus --> AssignSvc: ACK
deactivate Bus

AssignSvc --> Gateway: 200 OK\n{bug_id: "BUG-2026-0117",\nassignee: "dev.volkov"}
deactivate AssignSvc

Gateway --> QA: 200 OK\n{bug_id, assignee}
deactivate Gateway

== Асинхронная отправка уведомлений ==

Bus -> NotifyWorker: consume(BugAssigned)
activate NotifyWorker

NotifyWorker -> NotifyWorker: Формирование\nсписка получателей

NotifyWorker -> NotifyApi: sendNotification(dev.volkov,\n"Вам назначен BUG-2026-0117")
activate NotifyApi
NotifyApi --> NotifyWorker: delivered
deactivate NotifyApi

NotifyWorker -> DB: UPDATE notification_queue\nSET status='delivered'
activate DB
DB --> NotifyWorker: OK
deactivate DB

deactivate NotifyWorker

@enduml
